<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge"/>
  <title>Event Decline</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .email-container {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #c0392b;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .event-details {
      margin-top: 20px;
      padding: 10px;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    .event-details ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .event-details li {
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
    .footer {
      font-size: 12px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #aaa;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <h1>Hi {{userName}},</h1>
    <p>We regret to inform you that you have not been selected to participate in the event <strong>{{eventTitle}}</strong>.</p>

    <div class="event-details">
      <p>Event details:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Event Name:</strong> {{eventTitle}}</li>
        <li><strong>Date:</strong> {{eventDate}}</li>
        <li><strong>Time:</strong> {{eventTime}}</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <p>We truly appreciate your interest and encourage you to stay connected for future opportunities.</p>

    <p>Best regards,<br />Event Management Team</p>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>If you have any questions, feel free to contact us at support@eventmanagement.com</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
